      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DINGLE GREY (3) settled just off the speed then although a bit wayward cleared right away from a maiden field when resuming over this distance at Wyong last start. Lightly raced filly who has the scope to take this next step. BONDASONG (1) continues to race well deep into the maiden prep. Had little peace up front and only succumbed close to home over this trip at Wyong last time out. Might find this a shade easier and on a nine-day back-up makes plenty of appeal. CHARLINA (2) led and kicked right away only to be nailed on the line over 900m at Newcastle recently. Honest filly who will give backers a great sight again. WHISPERING RUPERT (5) is back from a brief spell. Might find this a bit sharp but with a gun run from gate one he can sneak into the frame. FARNCIFUL (6) is up on class but has been in the money at all three 1000m runs - must be respected.",
